- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is relevant as the paper proposes novel spectral bounds and locality sensitive hashing techniques for efficient community detection. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possible category as the paper deals with analyzing and optimizing the behavior of a dynamic system (the evolving network). 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is a possible category as the paper employs machine learning techniques (spectral clustering, locality sensitive hashing) for community detection.
